org.swerverobotics.library.interfaces

Interface I2cDeviceSynchUser

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    II2cDeviceClientUser
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AdaFruitBNO055IMU

    public interface I2cDeviceSynchUser
    I2cDeviceSynchUser allows one to retrieve an underlying I2cDeviceSynch from an a client of the latter. Such objects usually represent an semantic layer for an I2c sensor or actuator.
